    <h1>FestPack</h1>
    <div class="article">
      <p>This is a side project which is focused on simplifying the booking process for concerts and festivals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="article">
      <p>Normally when someone wants to attend a concert in another city, they would need to take care of the following:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Finding out in which cities do your favorite artists are having concerts</li>
        <li>Figure out which websites are providing concert tickets for this event.</li>
        <li>Compare the prices of different ticket types and by estimating other expenses you will have during this trip, try to decide on which ticket type you would like to get.</li>
        <li>Find a transportation option that suits your needs and budget.</li>
        <li>Find an accommodation option that is close to the event venue and suits your needs, and budget.</li>
        <li>Go through registration and payment processes of multiple websites in order to book the concert ticket, flight ticket, and hotel.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="article">
      <p>The whole process is very time and effort consuming. What FestPack does is, it knows the favorite artists of the user (which can either be imported from Spotify or added by the user), and it simplifies this process.
  Using FestPack users can check out different packages that were prepared for them, based on their music taste and location. These packages contain the transportation, accommodation and concert ticket. The user only sees one price for the whole package which allows them to easily judge whether it is within their budget or not.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Customization</h2>
    <div class="article with-video">
      <div><p>The potential user group of this application covers almost everyone who loves live music. Thus, there is a large difference in preferences between users regarding concert tickets, hotel types, and transportation choice.</p>
        <br>
        <p>FestPack provides multiple options (bronze, silver, and gold) differing from most affordable to the highest quality in order to serve the needs of all users. It is possible to choose the tier for the concert ticket, hotel, and transportation separately which allows further customization.</p>
      </div>
