    <h2>Bookmarks</h2>
    <div class="article with-video">
      <p>Attending a concert mostly requires some planning beforehand, like checking your calendar, considering your budget, or asking friends to see if anyone else is attending the same concert as you are planning. Therefore, it is not always possible to book such a package on the spot, users need some time to think. When browsing a package, it is possible to bookmark it and then the user can come back to that package from the profile page at any time.</p>
      <div>
