    </div>

    <h2>Artists</h2>
    <div class="article with-video">
      <p>FestPack keeps the list of the user’s favorite artists in the Artists tab. In this tab, users can search for artists and add them to their list as well. By tapping on a particular artist, it is possible to get more information about the artist and also see all the upcoming concerts from this artist as packages, which one can book immediately.</p>
