    <h2>Alerts and Filters</h2>
    <div class="article with-video">
      <div>
        <p>FestPack allows users to search/filter the packages based on artist, date, or budget. Based on search criteria, users can also set up an alert and the application will notify the user when there is a new matching result.</p>
        <br>
        <p>This feature allows users to catch deals from flights, hotels or concert tickets. While providing value to the user, this feature also provides a good way to gain returning customers.</p>
      </div>
