        <p>FestPack provides a single point of contact for the user’s complete trip. Users get to handle the payments for concert tickets, hotels, and transportation at the same time. This saves the user time both in terms of payment processes and also regarding registration processes that are mostly required by websites providing such services.</p>
        <br>
        <p>FestPack also provides the option to sign in using a Spotify account, which further reduces the entry barrier to the application.</p>
